USAGE INSTRUCTIONS:
==================
1. Copy this file to: src/pages/in_media/[your-article-slug]/index.astro
2. Update the Props interface values in the frontmatter
3. Replace the <slot /> content with your article content
4. Add videoUrl or articleUrl as needed

